title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES for Support Programme for Urban Reforms Bihar

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES for Support Programme for Urban Reforms Bihar) is a component of Support Programme for Urban Reforms in Bihar reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £22,952,457. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Basic drinking water supply and basic sanitation, Public finance management (PFM), Democratic participation and civil society, Urban development and management. , with the following implementing partners: IPE Global Private Limited, PwC. The start date is 01-05-2009 and the end date is 31-03-2017.
